descriptionNullable:
Jajanan Tradisional Jawa Tengah is dataset contains images of traditional snacks in Central Java. This dataset has 6 classes, such as  
1. Grontol
2. Lanting
3. Lumpia
4. Putu Ayu
5. Serabi Solo
6. Wajik

Collection Methodology
This dataset was collected from Google Images using selenium and python from this tutorial https://www.analyticsvidhya.com/blog/2020/08/web-scraping-selenium-with-python/
